snippet.title: Did Amber Rose RUIN 21 Savage?
snippet.description:
Did Amber Rose ruin 21 Savage? - 21 Savage is an artist who came up on his dark image, and his image has nothing but helped him rise to fame. 21 Savage is known for making that ''murder music'' as I would like to call it, but ever since he got together with Amber Rose - a lot of people have lost touch with 21. There's been a lot of discussions about that Amber Rose ruined 21 Savage and his image, and in this video I talk exactly about that and give my thoughts on the situation.

In this video I talk about whether I think Amber Rose ruined 21 Savage and his image, or not. 

Follow me on Twitter - https://twitter.com/BlackySpeakz

Instrumental in the background made by ORIGAMI and Matrix Mason - 

Origami's channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCmcF_CZ4oA3MkFdUZ5friXA/videos?disable_polymer=1

Matrix Mason's channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC252CWks988tggNsqrGz7bA/videos?disable_polymer=1

A lot of people have been asking what microphone I use in my videos, I use the ''Blue Yeti''. Link to buy the microphone (this is an affiliate link) - http://amzn.to/2fyeIzy
